data.description: Nestled in a charming gated community St James Park in Ocala, Florida, this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, constructed in 2017, effortlessly combines modern comfort with a prime location. Just 20 minutes from the renowned World Equestrian Center and a short 15-minute drive to Downtown Ocala, this residence offers the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and proximity to key attractions. The thoughtfully designed interior showcases a contemporary open concept, with a spacious living area seamlessly flowing into a well-appointed kitchen. This home features an indoor laundry room.The three bedrooms provide ample space for family or guests, while the master suite boasts a private oasis with an ensuite bathroom. Outside, the home is surrounded by the lush greenery of a well-maintained neighborhood, creating a serene backdrop for outdoor activities. With its strategic location offering quick access to both the equestrian center and the vibrant heart of Ocala, this home presents an ideal opportunity for those seeking a harmonious balance between convenience and a peaceful residential setting. Seller open to helping with closing costs.
